column5: This yrs.trip has come and gone 6 guys in camp 743 walleyes and 76 pike. I have booked the same week next yr 2013 first week in July. If you are a small group or a single. we maybe able to get you on this fly in to northern Quebec we have two camps booked and as of right now we have 3 openings in one camp and 4 in the other . If you are interested E-mail me [email protected] This is a great way to get introduced to a very good fly in trip. must of the guys who take this trip end up booking a trip for there group on their own I will give you all the info Thanks Ron https://www.walleyecentral.com/forums...c/progress.gif
